news/tis-the-election-season-again/article_2333ae6a-0ed5-53a7-9d80-31b63f3896c8.html|work=The Journal|date=December 3, 2018|accessdate=December 5, 2018}}</ref>\n*[[Joe Manchin]], incumbent U.S. Senator and former Governor of West Virginia<ref>{{cite news|url = https://www.politico.com/story/2019/09/03/joe-manchin-wont-run-for-governor-of-west-virginia-1479602|work = [[Politico]]|title = Joe Manchin won't run for governor of West Virginia|date = September 3, 2019|accessdate = September 3, 2019|last = Levine|first = Marianne}}</ref>\n\n=== Endorsements ===\n{{Endorsements box\n|title=Stephen Smith\n|list=\n;Federal politicians\n* [[Elizabeth Warren]], U.S. Senator (D-MA)<ref>{{cite web |last1=McElhinny |first1=Brad |title=Elizabeth Warren pitches an early endorsement for Stephen Smith's campaign for governor |url=http://wvmetronews.com/2019/09/09/elizabeth-warren-pitches-an-early-endorsement-for-stephen-smiths-campaign-for-governor/ |website=WV MetroNews |date=September 9, 2019 |quote=\u201cI\u2019m proud to endorse Stephen\u2019s bid for governor, and his team\u2019s efforts to run candidates up and down the ballot,\u201d Warren stated.}}</ref> \n;Organizations\n* 90 for 90<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.90for90.org/2020-candidates-west-virginia|title=2020 Candidates West Virginia|website=90 for 90|accessdate=March 28, 2020}}</ref>\n* Blue America<ref name=\"herald dispatch stephen smith\">{{cite web|url=https://www.herald-dispatch.com/elections/wv_candidates/w-va-governor-candidate-stephen-smith-d/article_47888dae-6188-11ea-814f-2f7f2d8c3d3d.html|title=W.Va. Governor candidate: Stephen Smith (D)|journal=The Herald Dispatch|date=March 8, 2020|accessdate=March 28, 2020}}</ref>\n* More than Addiction<ref name=\"herald dispatch stephen smith\"/>\n* [[People for the American Way]] - Next Up<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.pfaw.org/next-up-victory-fund/candidates|title=Next Up Endorses Young Progressive Candidates|website=People for the American Way|accessdate=March 28, 20